      "writtenOn": "2017-04-06T21:19:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Does it ever matter what this is initialized to?  The Chrome model seems to be: set as premul until we have finished filling in all of the pixels, then mark as opaque if it is opaque.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 204,
        "startChar": 21,
